<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />！<delay frames="30" />
你別再固執啦，<delay8 />
快主動去道歉吧！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" />才不要！<size value="100" /><20_2 arg="4" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說不要就是不要！<delay frames="30" />
我不懂這樣有什麼意義！<delay20 />
為什麼我非得去道歉不可啊？<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
你不該說這種話啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對方都已經那樣說了，<delay20 />
再來你只要主動低頭，<delay8 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />事情不就解決了嗎？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼跟什麼啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />真是不敢相信<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
搞得好像全都是我的錯一樣！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />事情都已經變成這樣了，<delay20 />
不管誰對誰錯都無所謂了吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你們任何一方都不肯低頭，<delay8 />
事情不就僵在那裡了嗎！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是說，<delay20 />你想跟對方互毆一場？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃！？<delay20 />
互毆？<delay frames="40" />
你是指<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拳拳到肉的那種？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="30" />
要是你已經有所覺悟了，我是不會阻止你<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，互毆很痛喔～！<delay frames="40" />還會流血喔～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咿～！<delay frames="40" />
我不能見血啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />而且我也怕痛～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真沒辦法<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
看來我還是只能主動去道歉啦！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是要這樣！<delay frames="30" />
所謂的爭執呢，<delay20 />
其實早點讓事情落幕的人才是贏家！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搶先主動低頭，<delay8 />
這樣絕對比較帥啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我總覺得<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，你真的好厲害啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有種<delay8 />超～級可靠的感覺！<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是個讓人費心的孩子<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />
你也講講她啦！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">去道歉吧</message>
	<message label="011_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不用道歉也沒關係</message>
	<message label="011_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我有點急事……</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<20_2 arg="5" />
怎麼連你也這麼說！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚哇～！<delay20 />
你們都不肯跟我同一國～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是那樣啦，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><delay frames="30" />
<tag a="110" b="3" />是希望<delay20 />你們趕快和好，<delay8 />
這樣才能再看到你的笑容啊！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對吧？<delay20 />我說的沒錯吧？</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是這樣嗎<20_2 arg="5" /><tag a="110" b="0" />？<20_2 arg="5" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="75" />嘻嘻。<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道了！<delay20 />
那我就<delay20 />去道歉吧！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" />為了等待我
露出笑容的粉絲，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也得變得成熟一點才行！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這樣！<delay20 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />就是這股氣魄！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="6" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />謝謝你！<delay frames="30" />
<20_2 arg="3" />真是幫了大忙啊！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />可以嗎？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />喂、<delay20 />喂！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />原來你願意站在我這邊啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />決定了！<delay frames="40" />
我就去<delay8 />找對方道歉吧！<20_3 arg="5" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然<tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
已經願意相信我沒有錯，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我覺得<delay8 />這件事就不用計較了！</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的假的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<20_3 arg="5" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真沒想到，<delay20 />你比我想得還要成熟！<20_2 arg="7" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不錯嘛，<delay20 />很帥氣喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就趁改變心意前<delay8 />趕快去吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />～～～～！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />我絕～對、<20_2 arg="5" /><delay20 /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />絕～～對<delay frames="40" />不會道歉！<10_4 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是<delay8 />心意已決喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～<delay frames="30" />
這下<delay8 />感覺得費一番工夫啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_1 arg="N0&gt;N1, N1&gt;N0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像你這樣類型的人……<delay20 />
比起這種島嶼，<delay8 />
應該更喜歡大都市才對吧？</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊～<delay20 />打算在出道的時候
打著「原‧無人島居民個性派偶像」<delay8 />
這樣的名號當作宣傳！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是不建立起自己的風格，<delay20 />
可是無法在這個業界生存的！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經營偶像……<delay8 />就像是一場野外求生啊！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是我問你，<delay20 />
這樣你要怎麼跟上最新潮流之類的啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這種島上，<delay8 />雜誌數量屈指可數，<delay20 />
就連電視節目<delay8 />也只有那幾個吧？</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！？<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的耶～！<delay20 />
怎麼辦～？<delay8 />這樣超～不妙的啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔～<delay8 />既然如此，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就只能由我來引領潮流了！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔喔，<delay20 />真是積極正面啊～！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我倒是挺喜歡你這種性格的喔！</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那……<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
你就當攝影師！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="8" />然後呢，<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
<20_2 arg="6" />你就是我的製作人！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你們兩個可要好好地<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />把我的魅力傳達出去喔！<delay frames="40" />
拜託你們囉～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼會發展呈這個狀況啊！？<delay frames="30" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，你也勸勸她吧！<delay20 /><20_3 arg="4" /></message>
	<message label="107_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />辦不到啦</message>
	<message label="107_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會努力的</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 />連<tag a="110" b="3" />
都說辦不到了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你們兩個不用那麼謙虛啊～！<20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～耶！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="33" />偶像計畫，<delay20 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開始囉～～～～！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的假的啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="4" />算啦，<delay8 />反正她應該玩一下就膩了吧？<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所～<delay8 />以～<delay8 />說～！<delay frames="40" />
就算你現在在那邊擔心
自己的歌曲太過暢銷，<delay8 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也沒有意義啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就叫你<delay8 />先等自己出了單曲之後
再想這個問題啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />「<tag a="110" b="5" />」？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，你剛剛<delay20 />
說了「<tag a="110" b="5" />」嗎？</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />啊……<delay8 />嗯，<delay20 />
我好像是說了沒錯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼了嗎？</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～真的假的，<delay8 />太猛了吧！？<delay20 />
聽起來超～帥氣的耶！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從今天開始，我也想跟著用～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你根本就已經拿去用了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不介意這種事啦，<delay8 />
想要就拿去吧！</message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的嗎！？<delay20 />好棒～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />可是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我開始使用之後，<delay8 />
我的粉絲們開始跟著用，<delay20 />
沒多久，<delay8 />就在全世界掀起一陣熱潮<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後，<delay8 />大家可能都會誤以為
是我最先開始用「<tag a="110" b="5" />」的！<delay frames="30" />
該怎麼辦啊～！？</message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以啦，<delay20 />就跟你說
擔這種心也沒用了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～<delay20 />算了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
